title: I See Death Around The Corner w/ Alex Fumero & The Tragic Tale of PNB Rock
itunes:title: I See Death Around The Corner w/ Alex Fumero & The Tragic Tale of PNB Rock
description:
In this Gangster Chronicles double feature we sit down with American Me podcast host Alex Fumero and discuss the murders and controversy surrounding the classic movie and why it may have been more fiction than fact. Eiht, Steele and James then dive into the murder of rapper PNB Rock. Make sure to subscribe to the American Me podcast with Alex Fumero https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/more-than-a-movie-american-me/id1643773613 "
